      "description": "Total tokens and estimated cost across all runs for the selected Linear issue. Cost is estimated at gpt-5.5 pricing: input $5.00 / output $30.00 / cached $0.50 per M tokens. Totals are summed from codex.sse_event response.completed logs within the dashboard time range.",
